text: Valkeakoski is a city in Finland. It is known for its paper industry. Nearby municipalities are Akaa, Hattula, Hämeenlinna, Kangasala, Lempäälä and Pälkäne. In 1973, Sääksmäki was merged with Valkeakoski. ==Other websites== Category:Cities in Finland Category:Municipalities of Pirkanmaa
title: Valkeakoski
